{"tid":232251,"cid":10,"subCid":0,"title":"幻羽天龍?神奇猥瑣佬 又出來昆錢啦(有證據)","createTime":"2017-05-06T15:26:38.000Z","updateTime":"2017-06-15T07:27:04.000Z","uid":101962,"like":10,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"f9264f56db982d7d9aba15dc82fffe46c937ea1a","tid":232251,"uid":101962,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-06T15:26:38.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/219492/page/1\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/219492/page/1</a><br />\n<br />\n[一年一度][天龍私服] 幻羽天龍 <br />\n真係一年一度 一年執一次 .<br />\n下面有齊晒證據.<br />\n你仲要死雞撐飯蓋<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.2000fun.com/thread-4990582-1-1.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.2000fun.com%2Fthread-4990582-1-1.html&d=Lu%2FYWbP3Pl%2BxzjQ0by0jcv7vEz4FU%2Bq4m%2F6ZFrWLoTs%3D&h=80e4a0b1\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.2000fun.com/thread-4990582-1-1.html</a><br />\n2012年 開個server 閃服 執埋<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.2000fun.com/thread-5515023-1-1.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.2000fun.com%2Fthread-5515023-1-1.html&d=Lu%2FYWbP3Pl%2BxzjQ0by0jcv7vEz4FU%2Bq4m%2F6ZFrWLoTs%3D&h=acc68cb9\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.2000fun.com/thread-5515023-1-1.html</a><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://forum5.hkgolden.com/view.aspx?message=5297352\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fforum5.hkgolden.com%2Fview.aspx%3Fmessage%3D5297352&d=Lu%2FYWbP3Pl%2BxzjQ0by0jcv7vEz4FU%2Bq4m%2F6ZFrWLoTs%3D&h=2eabd449\" target=\"_blank\">http://forum5.hkgolden.com/view.aspx?message=5297352</a><br />\n2014年 <span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">HKTLBB</span></strong></span> 又稱長久 開左一陣又執 閃服<br />\n神奇猥瑣佬 當年昆左我地大家幾多錢?<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.2000fun.com/thread-5547870-1-1.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.2000fun.com%2Fthread-5547870-1-1.html&d=Lu%2FYWbP3Pl%2BxzjQ0by0jcv7vEz4FU%2Bq4m%2F6ZFrWLoTs%3D&h=7cd61248\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.2000fun.com/thread-5547870-1-1.html</a><br />\n2015年 唔知咩名私服 開左一陣又執 再一個閃服 <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n到今年2017 <span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">神奇猥瑣佬</span></span> 再次出現昆錢 .<br />\n<br />\n又係<span style=\"color: red;\">惡人谷</span> 2000FUN又係<span style=\"color: red;\">l2003201</span><br />\n<br />\n唔好話係借人地AC呀 你個GM叫<span style=\"color: red;\">Kaden </span><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><br />\nl2003201</span> 的小屋- 巴哈姆特<br />\n<a href=\"https://home.gamer.com.tw/l2003201\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhome.gamer.com.tw%2Fl2003201&d=Lu%2FYWbP3Pl%2BxzjQ0by0jcv7vEz4FU%2Bq4m%2F6ZFrWLoTs%3D&h=b9085099\" target=\"_blank\">https://home.gamer.com.tw/l2003201</a><br />\n勇者資訊. 帳號：l2003201; 暱稱：<span style=\"color: red;\">Kaden</span>; 稱號：尚未取得<br />\n<br />\n唔好話咁岩得咁橋啦.神奇猥瑣佬. <br />\n親友ser唔怪你, 但你親友到打輸交就封人地AC<br />\n邊個忍得你落呀 <span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">神奇猥瑣佬</span></span>."},{"pid":"01e426bc549943ba562016e81ca59cb77539b45a","tid":232251,"uid":101962,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-06T15:31:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"628827f9fd7263fc8879a3d61a5d90fbccd6259c","tid":232251,"uid":101962,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-06T15:49:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src