mal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d3523a8c38940f71510e46ee6979569037bd4d17","tid":232251,"uid":101962,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-07T18:02:09.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://github.com/l2003201 \" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fgithub.com%2Fl2003201%20&d=Lu%2FYWbP3Pl%2BxzjQ0by0jcv7vEz4FU%2Bq4m%2F6ZFrWLoTs%3D&h=f16324f7\" target=\"_blank\">https://github.com/l2003201 </a><br />\n<br />\n又一個I2003201又叫Kaden <br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">如果咁都話個帳號任人開 只要你阿爺英文名叫Kaden</span><br />\n<br />\n咁多個數目唔揀 揀2003201? 叫Kaden? 唔係一個網站, 係幾個網站都係叫Kaden<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/84310/page/1\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/84310/page/1</a><br />\n<br />\n大家留意下入面<br />\nA1. 有，依家得返傭兵可以用，但每次Game更新之後都要更新返個V_hk.dat先用得返，可以用Updater download最新既傭兵同埋同步返Server既檔案就可以直接用啦～<br />\n<a href=\"https://github.com/l2003201/WL-Updater/raw/master/updater.exe\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fgithub.com%2Fl2003201%2FWL-Updater%2Fraw%2Fmaster%2Fupdater.exe&d=Lu%2FYWbP3Pl%2BxzjQ0by0jcv7vEz4FU%2Bq4m%2F6ZFrWLoTs%3D&h=28bb565a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://github.com/l2003201/WL-Updater/raw/master/updater.exe</a><br />\n<br />\nUser Name: <span style=\"color: red;\">歐叭 </span>  link入面有埋 I2003201 <br />\n<br />\n咁都叫<span style=\"color: red;\">帳號任人開 只要你阿爺英文名叫Kaden</span>??<br />\n<br />\n打手親友團, 查清楚理據先好出聲講野?"}]}